releases.description: Initial Release. Added the aether and its highlands. Updated the Aether Highlands to make it look more like the mod. Command: /execute at aether:aether run to username 1 100 0.

Initial Release. Changed the color of foliages. Added the aether portal. Portal Structure: # = glowstone, ? = water, ####, #??#, #??#, #??#, ####. Warning: You might need structure voids to help the water stay in place.
The Trees, Highlands and Portals Update. Coming Soon.
